rect.id: We are going to ask you all the necessary questions allowing us to turn your requests into specific tasks. When all the tasks are outlined, we will proceed with the correct solution installation. Then we need to create CRM users and set up work with mail and file storage.

We are going to train your staff to be productive at work with the system. Plus, during the agreed time after the successful CRM implementation, the UDS team will be in touch with you to handle any CRM issues.

From the basic settings, we will move on to creating CRM functionality to unite and streamline the main business processes of your sales department and display this functionality in an easy-to-read and suitable way. Also, we need to provide employees with different levels of access to the system according to their responsibilities. After that, your team can start using your CRM.

For those whose needs go beyond the UDS Quick Start Sales, we provide a range of additional services. You can book some of them right away, for example, transferring data from your `old` system. Or you can do it after checking the quality of our work, for example, creating a user-friendly portal for your customers or integrating your CRM with some third-party tools popular within your company. If one day you decide to expand the capabilities of your Dynamics 365 Sales, we will surely consult you on worthwhile actions for your particular case.
